---
description: gstack contributor workflow for Cursor
globs:
  - "SKILL.md.tmpl"
  - "browse/SKILL.md.tmpl"
  - "**/*.tmpl"
  - "browse/src/**/*.ts"
  - "scripts/**/*.ts"
  - "test/**/*.ts"
  - "**/SKILL.md"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use Bun commands from the repo root.
- Default validation flow after edits:
  1) `bun run gen:skill-docs`
  2) `bun run skill:check`
  3) `bun test`
- Treat `SKILL.md` files as generated artifacts:
  - edit corresponding `SKILL.md.tmpl` source files
  - run `bun run gen:skill-docs` after template changes
  - keep template and regenerated docs in the same commit
- Prefer `bun run eval:select` before running costed evals.
- Do not run paid evals (`test:e2e`, `test:evals`) unless explicitly requested.
- Follow workspace conventions in `CLAUDE.md` and `CONTRIBUTING.md`.
